{"parse":{"title":"Monstrous Felblood Snapper","pageid":158301,"wikitext":{"*":"{{stub/Item}}<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|name=Monstrous Felblood Snapper\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_44\n|stack=20\n|quality=common\n|qitem=yes\n|ilvl=70\n}}</onlyinclude>\n'''Monstrous Felblood Snapper''' is a [[quest objective]] of the [[fishing]] [[daily quest]] {{questlong|Neutral|70 Daily|Felblood Fillet}}.\n\n== Source ==\nIt can be caught in the [[Pools of Aggonar]] in [[Hellfire Peninsula]] or at the [[Magma Fields]] in [[Shadowmoon Valley]].\n\n== Patch changes ==\n{{Patch 2.4.0|note=Added}}\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|34867}}\n{{elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/monstrous_felblood_snapper.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common quest items]]"}}}